<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>About - CaféCierge</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick.min.css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick-theme.min.css"/>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
      color: #343a40;
    }

    h1 {
      border-bottom: 2px solid #343a40;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .image-container {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .image-container img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .personal-photo {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .slick-carousel img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .slider{
      display: none;
    }
    .slider.slick-initialized{
      display: block; /*slick-initializedが付与されたら表示*/
    }

    .personal-photo img {
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
    }

    .contact-info {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="content">
    <h1>About CaféCierge</h1>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>My Mission</h2>
      <p>Welcome to CaféCierge! My name is Yûta Masuda, and my mission is to connect coffee lovers with the best cafes around. Whether you're looking for a cozy place to work, a stylish spot for a date, or simply the best coffee in town, I've got you covered.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section image-container slick-carousel">
      <% (1..20).each do |i| %>
        <div>
          <img src="<%= asset_path("cafe_mission_#{i}.jpg") %>" alt="Our Mission Image <%= i %>">
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>What I Offer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Comprehensive cafe listings with detailed information</li>
        <li>User reviews and ratings to help you choose the best spot</li>
        <li>Reservation system to secure your favorite table</li>
        <li>Personalized recommendations based on your preferences</li>
        <li>Community features to connect with other coffee enthusiasts</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section image-container">
      <img src="<%= asset_path('cafe_offers.jpg') %>" alt="What I Offer">
    </div>

    <div class="section personal-photo">
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <img src="<%= asset_path('your_photo.jpg') %>" alt="Your Photo">
      <h3>Yûta Masuda</h3>
      <p>I am the creator and developer of CaféCierge. My passion for coffee and web development inspired me to create this platform to help others find their perfect cafe experience.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section contact-info">
      <h2>Contact Me</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions, suggestions, or just want to say hi, feel free to reach out to me at <a href="mailto:support@cafecierge.com">support@cafecierge.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    $(document).ready(function(){
      $('.slick-carousel').not('.slick-initialized').slick({
        autoplay: true,
        autoplaySpeed: 2000,
        dots: true,
        infinite: true,
        speed: 500,
        fade: true,
        cssEase: 'linear'
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>